query:
INSERT INTO propertyDeepSearch (propertyId, overviewNotes, issues) VALUES (
  (SELECT id FROM properties WHERE addressLine1 = '1513 NW 24th Ave' AND city = 'Fort Lauderdale' ORDER BY id DESC LIMIT 1),
  'PROPERTY: 1513 NW 24th Ave, Fort Lauderdale, FL 33311
Single-Family Home | Built 1954 | 4 Bed / 2 Bath | 1,602 sq ft

DECEASED OWNER: Billy Dale Williams
Death Date: September 2, 2006 (Age 64-65)
Previous Address: 2300 NW 38th Ter, Lauderdale Lakes, FL 33311
Phone: (954) 687-3030 / (954) 588-1121
Burial: American Burial & Cremation Center At Jennings Funeral Home
Obituary: Sun-Sentinel, September 4, 2006

PROBATE STATUS: ⚠️ PROBATE CASE FILED
• Deceased: Billy Dale Williams (September 2, 2006)
• Likely Case: PRC06-XXXXX (requires verification)
• Status: Probate likely closed, property transferred to heirs
• Current Ownership: Estate heirs or beneficiaries

VALUATION:
• Redfin Estimate: $420,515 ($262/sq ft)
• Homes.com Estimate: $449,967 ($280/sq ft)
• Average: $435,241
• Last Sale (1978): $9,000
• Total Appreciation: 4,566% - 4,900% (+$411,515 to $440,967)

PROPERTY TAXES:
• 2024: $7,782 (+8.6%)
• 2023: $7,163 (+11.3%)
• 2022: $6,433 (+479.3% - reassessment)
• 2021: $1,111
• Status: Current and Paid

CODE VIOLATIONS: ✅ None
• No open violations
• Compliant with all codes

PROPERTY CONDITION:

• Well-maintained

• Extraordinary appreciation potential

2. Obtain probate documents (will, inventory, discharge order)
3. Identify heirs from estate documents
4. Verify current ownership via certified deed
5. Contact heirs to discuss property status',
  '[]'
);
